data.description: Beautifully updated brick ranch in a nice quiet neighborhood! Feel at home entering in with gorgeous hardwood and vinyl plank throughout! This home was completely updated in 2020! The floor plan on the main offers 3 bedrooms- one of which is a master with ensuite half bath, a common full bath, a large living room with a big window that allows lots of light in and a eat in kitchen! The kitchen has asthetically pleasing cabinets and a full set of stainless appliances that will stay! More to mention with a walkout basement that entails a spacious L-shaped family room, laundry room, and 3/4 bath!  Outdoors you will be pleased to have a level backyard that is fenced with a patio! This perfect home also has plenty of parking with a long driveway and an attached garage! Other updates include a new roof in 2023! The HVAC also had the circuit board replaced in 2020 and AC was cleared in 2023! MOVE IN READY! Contingent on sellers home of choice passing contingencies. .Come and love!
